name: L-phenylalanine:NAD+ oxidoreductase (deaminating)
rxn_str: phe__L_c + h2o_c + nad_c <=> phpyr_c + nh3_c + nadh_c + 2.0 h_c

name: Anthranilate,NADH:oxygen oxidoreductase (1,2-hydroxylating, deaminating, decarboxylating)
rxn_str: anth_c + o2_c + nadh_c + 2.0 h_c <=> catechol_c + nh3_c + co2_c + nad_c

name: 4-Coumarate:Coa Ligase (AMP-Forming)
rxn_str: atp_c + coa_c + T4hcinnm_c <=> amp_c + ppi_c + coucoa_c

name: Malonyl-CoA:4-coumaroyl-CoA malonyltransferase (cyclizing)
rxn_str: 3 malcoa_c + coucoa_c + 3 h_c <=> 4 coa_c + resv_c + 4 co2_c

name: Tryptophanase (L-tryptophan)
rxn_str: h2o_c + trp__L_c <=> indole_c + nh3_c + h_c + pyr_c
